description: An IRI or similar locator for a request or discussion of an ontology term.
The 'tracker item' can associate a tracker with a specific ontology term.

definition source: Person: Jie Zheng, Chris Stoeckert, Alan Ruttenberg
example of usage: the URI for an OBI Terms ticket at sourceforge, such as https://sourceforge.net/p/obi/obi-terms/772/
term editor: Person: Jie Zheng, Chris Stoeckert, Alan Ruttenberg

label: term tracker item
